# Welcome to the Kui Client Template

After you have [instantiated this GitHub template](https://github.com/kui-shell/KuiClientTemplate/generate), and git cloned your repository, you can start developing your custom Kui client.

```sh
npm ci
npm run watch
npm run open
```

Look [here](https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/kui/wiki) for some customization ideas.

## Notebooks

This is a Kui notebook. It is just a shell session, with some commentary, that has been saved via File->Save. To add a commentary block, execute the command [`#`](#kuiexec?command=%23).
